verbose_text: However, extracellular application of THL (10 muM) significantly reduced the inhibitory effect of cocaine on GABA B IPSCs (extra-THL = 85.6% +/- 4.7% of control, n = 5; p = 0.009, paired t test; p < 0.05, one-way ANOVA, Bonferroni post hoc analysis; XREF_FIG).
evidence: THL (10 muM) significantly reduced the inhibitory effect of cocaine
